node.text:
Description

Deep Black Eyeliner/Lash Adhesive

Benefits:
 ✨Fast Drying✨
✨Waterproof✨
✨Long Lasting✨
✨Smooth to the touch✨

How to Apply: 

Step1: Shake well then  Apply the 2in1 liner/lash adhesive to your eyelids in the same way you’d apply eyeliner.

Step2: Wait a few seconds to allow the adhesive to become tacky.

Step3: Apply your Eyelashes or allow it to dry to use as regular eyeliner.

This eyeliner pen is a great addition to strip lashes. Can be used with any strip lash.  Put on eyeliner and strip sticks to eyeliner. No more strip glue, no more struggle, no more crooked lashes, and no more build up on strip from glue. It’s a games changer!!

node.title: Luxury Black Liquid Diamond Eyeliner 2in1 Pen Glue For Lashes Adhesive

node.text:
2in1 Deep Black Eyeliner/Lash Adhesive (Gold with diamonds)
 
Clear Eyelash Adhesive (Silver with Diamonds)
@lashedcosmetics (Link in bio) 
Benefits:
 ✨Fast Drying✨
✨Waterproof✨
✨Long Lasting✨
✨Smooth to the touch✨

How to Apply: 

Step1: Shake well then  Apply the 2in1 liner/lash adhesive to your eyelids in the same way you’d apply eyeliner.

Step2: Wait a few seconds to allow the adhesive to become tacky.

Step3: Apply your Eyelashes or allow it to dry to use as regular eyeliner.

This eyeliner pen is a great addition to strip lashes. Can be used with any strip lash.  Put on eyeliner and strip sticks to eyeliner. No more strip glue, no more struggle, no more crooked lashes, and no more build up on strip from glue. It’s a games changer!!
